Connect with WEbhool to get data from link url webhook when user send message.

----------------------------------------------------------------------
You need to have Line account to access Line chat application

1. Create new provider

Go to Messaging API
- Change icon, name and description of your chat bot

Save Channel secret token, Channel access token and bot id

-----------------------------------------------------------------------

Create folder to put files
-----------------------------------------------------------------------

- Command -

pip install virtualenv

virtualenv venv

venv\Scripts\activate  *important*

. code

pip install Flask #run server on local

pip install requests


------------------------------------------------------------------------

Download Ngrok (ngrok secure introspectable tunnels to localhost webhook development tool and debugging tool.)

ngrok http 200 >> get public url or webhook url (ex.  f52f0b68c90c.ngrok.io)

------------------------------------------------------------------------

